WEBVTT

00:00:00.520 --> 00:00:02.096
Siku.

00:00:02.120 --> 00:00:03.496
Damu.

00:00:03.520 --> 00:00:04.720
Hedhi.

00:00:05.440 --> 00:00:07.016
Uchafu.

00:00:07.040 --> 00:00:08.656
Siri.

00:00:08.680 --> 00:00:09.880
Kuficha.

00:00:10.400 --> 00:00:11.600
Kwanini?

00:00:12.760 --> 00:00:14.656
Utaratibu asilia kibaolojia

00:00:14.680 --> 00:00:18.496
ambao kila msichana na mwanamke
anapitia kila mwezi

00:00:18.520 --> 00:00:20.696
kwa karibia nusu ya maisha yake.

00:00:20.720 --> 00:00:23.416
Jambo ambalo ni la umuhimu mkubwa sana

00:00:23.440 --> 00:00:27.640
kiasi kwamba kupona na uenezwaji
wa spishi zetu unautegemea.

00:00:28.480 --> 00:00:30.320
Bado tunauchukulia kama mwiko.